      <title>华尔街认为能源股将迎来又一个充满挑战的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/wall-street-sours-on-energy-stocks-as-supply-worries-dominate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街认为能源股又将面临充满挑战的一年，因为分析师预计充足的石油供应将阻止地缘政治紧张局势加剧刺激原油价格大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/wall-street-sours-on-energy-stocks-as-supply-worries-dominate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 18:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
