      <title>在人们热切期待的 ETF 决定之前，比特币逆转了走势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/bitcoin-btc-reverses-course-ahead-of-eagerly-awaited-etf-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，比特币暴跌，导致该加密货币几乎抹去了今年头几天的所有涨幅，与传统资产的全球低迷表现的长期上涨背道而驰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/bitcoin-btc-reverses-course-ahead-of-eagerly-awaited-etf-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:36:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
